description: Biden administration officials said the U.S. won’t join any Israeli response to Iran’s attack and urged the Netanyahu government to avoid escalation.
title: Biden counsels Netanyahu to ‘slow things down’ after Iranian attack

description: Arab governments, already struggling to contain popular fury at the war in Gaza, pleaded for calm after Iran’s drone and missile attacks on Israel.
title: Arab nations call for restraint as Israel-Iran conflict intensifies

description: Iran’s attack against Israel was unprecedented in scope, but analysts said it was also clearly telegraphed and carefully choreographed to minimize death and destruction.
title: Iran crosses old red lines and sets ‘new equation’ with attack on Israel

description: In Jerusalem, a city rarely troubled by aerial attacks, the sounds of the interceptions rolled through like thunder. Air raid sirens wailed; people gathered on balconies, or pressed their faces to the windows, as fireballs lit up the sky.
title: Israelis recount worry, fear after night of Iran missile interceptions

description: The nightmare scenario Israeli leaders had long warned about — a direct attack from Iran — showcased the regional coalition and high-tech systems built to repel it.
title: Israel mulls response after U.S.-led alliance fends off Iranian barrage

description: Biden reassured Benjamin Netanyahu of U.S. commitment to Israel’s security after Iran’s unprecedented attack. Nearly all missiles and drones were intercepted, Israel said.
title: Live updates: U.S. helps Israel thwart Iranian attack of 300 drones and missiles

description: Iran said the attack — more than 300 drones and missiles — was retaliation for an Israeli strike on an Iranian diplomatic compound in Syria on April 1.
title: Why did Iran attack Israel? What to know about the strikes, U.S. response.

description: Cheap drones deployed as ‘eyes in the skies’ over Ukraine are transforming warfare, allowing operators to destroy expensive equipment or hunt and kill individual soldiers.
title: Drones are crowding Ukraine’s skies, largely paralyzing battlefield

description: A look at where Iranian drones and missiles hit in Israel.
title: Mapping the wide-scale Iranian drone and missile attacks
